oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Inside Nashville - J. G. Collie 80th Birthday Edition
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Recording of a special edition of Biff Collie's radio program Inside Nashville, dedicated to J. G. "Pop" Collie's 80th birthday.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: [Unidentified child's voice] introduces this recording for J. G. Collie's 80th birthday -- Inside Nashville jingle -- Biff Collie talks -- [Unidentified] wishes Collie a happy birthday -- [Unidentified group of children] sing happy birthday to J. G. Collie -- [Unidentified] wishes Collie a happy birthday and tells a story -- [Unidentified] talks about never partaking in drinking, smoking, or drugs and attributing this to how he has lived so long -- [Unidentified] talks and wishes Collie a happy birthday -- [Unidentified] wishes Collie a happy birthday -- Biff Collie talks about James Guthrie Collie being born 80 years ago today and talks about some of his other life achievements -- Biff Collie wishes his father happy birthday
